product.title: Lambert - The Gabrielle Vegan Leather Bag in Black
product.body_html: If versatility was a bag, we'd name it Gabrielle. Made with premium, PETA-certified vegan leather, it can easily be worn in 4 different ways by adjusting the straps: as a pouch, a shoulder bag, a belt bag across the body or at the waist. 13cm (height) x 21.5cm (length) x 4cm (depth).
